<section id="slide-org2ca0ad4">
<h3 id="org2ca0ad4">Unraveling an oracle</h3>
<ol>
<li class="fragment appear">oracle of doom or of salvation</li>
<li class="fragment appear">identify form</li>
<li class="fragment appear">Who is being condemned (saved)?</li>
<li class="fragment appear">Why?</li>
<li class="fragment appear">Form of punishment (deliverance)?</li>
<li class="fragment appear">Does it apply to all or a remnant?</li>
<li class="fragment appear">Pay attention to the view of God. Warrior? Judge? &#x2026;?</li>

</ol>
</section>
